{"tid":846174,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[Avios/ANA 里數] 有冇人有用Mileslife (邁生活)儲里數？","createTime":"2018-10-03T08:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T16:31:35.000Z","uid":61720,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8faae1b02e700d05d61c89cccb8bf4300ac7bef0","tid":846174,"uid":61720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱又開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食嘢用呢個app俾錢就可以儲里數~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個app可以揀儲邊個里數，大路啲就係avios或者ANA，冇asia miles儲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n迎新<br />\n－ 被推薦優惠：<br />\n只要註冊時輸入朋友推薦code，再於一個月內簽消費滿$299就有額外1000里！<br />\n<strong>推薦人同被推薦人都各有1000里</strong><br />\n當你喺指定餐廳食咗$300野，<br />\n&ndash; 如果Mileslife俾$2/里，即係150里<br />\n&ndash; 被推薦優惠 1000 里<br />\n<br />\n＝&gt;加埋即係食$300野就有1,150里<br />\n<br />\n儲夠9000里就可以換台北/高雄/台中/河內/峴港嘅機票<br />\n15000可以換泰國<br />\n20000可以換大阪/東京/名古屋/福岡<br />\n北海道要25000<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔想洗錢但想儲里數嘅<br />\n喺個app每簽到7日就可以抽里數，由10-200里<br />\n可以積少成多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAvios可以開household ac，最多連5個ac~啲分可以集埋一齊儲"},{"pid":"3be42b2e23ab714c1551499cf15483883152ef26","tid":846174,"uid":214185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"簽到七日個個由6月尾開始次次都唔過20miles<br />\n各位巴打最近抽到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"a5f1adf442d5198b272683ff07ed0e0ab13bf775","tid":846174,"uid":214185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"btw mileslife而家出咗個提醒簽卡功能都幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c8abd260b5d1d2aaa79a0346851c7835ce511e","tid":846174,"uid":61720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be42b2e23ab714c1551499cf15483883152ef26","tid":846